#  Variables found in codebase:
#    ✅ VITE_SUPABASE_URL       → src/lib/supabase.ts (Vite client)
#    ✅ VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY  → src/lib/supabase.ts (Vite client)
#    ✅ SUPABASE_SERVICE_KEY    → setup_supabase_tables.js (Node script)
# ==============================================================================


# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Supabase Public/Client Configuration
# (VITE_ prefix exposes these to the browser via Vite)
# 📍 Get from: Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → API
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

